WEBVTT

00:00:00.320 --> 00:01:35.400

00:01:40.105 --> 00:01:43.785
QINGSONG CEMENT FACTORY, WEIYANG CITY

00:01:43.865 --> 00:01:50.345
REFORM FOR GROWTH

00:02:00.665 --> 00:02:03.985
DRIVE SLOWLY, SAFETY FIRST

00:02:17.505 --> 00:02:20.105
Sir. Busy? Have a drink.

00:02:20.185 --> 00:02:21.145
No, thanks.

00:02:23.745 --> 00:02:24.985
Anyway,

00:02:25.065 --> 00:02:27.265
did the owner of the factory come today?

00:02:27.345 --> 00:02:28.665
Which owner?

00:02:28.745 --> 00:02:30.505
Mr. Song Qingsong.

00:02:31.105 --> 00:02:33.785
I don't know about that,
but you can't park your car there.

00:02:33.865 --> 00:02:35.385
If you're not here to get it fixed,
move it away.

00:02:35.465 --> 00:02:36.385
Understood?

00:02:37.025 --> 00:02:38.065
Get it fixed.

00:02:38.145 --> 00:02:39.145
I'm here to get it fixed.

00:02:39.225 --> 00:02:41.785
Look how damaged it is.
Check it and quote a price.

00:02:44.465 --> 00:02:45.545
You parked at a great spot.

00:02:49.145 --> 00:02:51.345
Your car is seriously damaged.

00:02:51.865 --> 00:02:53.185
Did the other person run away?

00:02:56.545 --> 00:02:57.905
Stop staring.

00:02:57.985 --> 00:02:59.385
You won't see Song here.

00:03:00.065 --> 00:03:00.905
Why is that?

00:03:00.985 --> 00:03:03.865
Those who can see Song
won't come to me and ask about him.

00:03:06.545 --> 00:03:07.905
But isn't it weird?

00:03:08.665 --> 00:03:10.745
The place is locked up tight.

00:03:10.825 --> 00:03:13.265
And the guard is strong.

00:03:13.345 --> 00:03:15.505
One might even say
he's guarding an armory.

00:03:15.585 --> 00:03:16.585
Have you not heard?

00:03:17.105 --> 00:03:18.465
There was a gang fight here two days ago.

00:03:18.545 --> 00:03:19.905
More than 200 men.

00:03:19.985 --> 00:03:21.505
It was huge.

00:03:21.585 --> 00:03:23.145
I lost some of my wrenches.

00:03:23.225 --> 00:03:25.505
A gang fight? With whom?

00:03:25.585 --> 00:03:26.745
Cripple Du.

00:03:27.265 --> 00:03:28.785
Song's rival.

00:03:28.865 --> 00:03:29.905
But why?

00:03:29.985 --> 00:03:32.665
For business. The business in the mine.

00:03:33.785 --> 00:03:34.825
The mine?

00:03:35.705 --> 00:03:36.905
Dongshan Mine?

00:03:37.825 --> 00:03:39.025
Do you see another mine in Weiyang?

00:03:42.065 --> 00:03:44.305
It's run by the government.
Very lucrative.

00:03:56.505 --> 00:03:58.625
QINGSONG CEMENT

00:04:16.705 --> 00:04:19.905
PATTIA FRONT DESK

00:04:19.985 --> 00:04:21.384
Uncle Ran,

00:04:21.465 --> 00:04:22.745
now that we have checked
the underground labyrinth,

00:04:22.825 --> 00:04:25.185
it's time to check the labyrinth upstairs.

00:04:25.985 --> 00:04:28.025
We need to change our method for that.

00:04:28.105 --> 00:04:29.065
Change our method?

00:04:29.665 --> 00:04:31.065
We'll use Tremeaux's algorithm.

00:04:31.145 --> 00:04:33.345
Tremor? Like land tremors?

00:04:34.065 --> 00:04:35.145
Here.

00:04:35.865 --> 00:04:39.105
Trémaux's algorithm
is the most time-intensive

00:04:39.185 --> 00:04:42.505
yet the most likely to succeed
among all labyrinth solvers.

00:04:42.585 --> 00:04:45.785
In short, take every route

00:04:45.865 --> 00:04:48.425
and mark them so that we don't make
the same mistake.

00:04:48.505 --> 00:04:51.105
In the end, we'll find the exit.

00:04:51.185 --> 00:04:53.985
To translate it
into our investigation, it means

00:04:54.065 --> 00:04:55.025
we have to first find a lead.

00:04:55.625 --> 00:04:58.425
Uncle Ran, you make it sound
too complicated.

00:04:58.505 --> 00:05:00.505
Forget about tremors. Just do this.

00:05:01.665 --> 00:05:03.865
This is the entrance. This is the exit.

00:05:04.465 --> 00:05:06.265
Now, you'll find the solution.

00:05:09.785 --> 00:05:10.785
Give it back.

00:05:25.465 --> 00:05:27.425
WEIYANG CITY DONGSHAN
MINE OPERATION CONTRACTOR TENDER DOCUMENT

00:05:27.505 --> 00:05:28.545
Come in.

00:05:35.585 --> 00:05:36.705
Mr. Song.

00:05:36.785 --> 00:05:37.745
Hear me out.

00:05:37.825 --> 00:05:38.865
Yesterday, I…

00:05:40.305 --> 00:05:42.265
You did well last night.

00:05:43.225 --> 00:05:44.625
You're smart.

00:05:47.145 --> 00:05:48.145
This is your reward.

00:05:49.305 --> 00:05:51.265
Mr. Song, I was just doing my job.

00:05:51.345 --> 00:05:52.465
So, take it.

00:05:52.545 --> 00:05:53.585
I…

00:05:54.265 --> 00:05:55.385
Thank you.

00:06:00.945 --> 00:06:02.585
When will you return the things
worth hundreds of thousands of yuan

00:06:02.665 --> 00:06:04.065
stolen from Yuanlongli?

00:06:04.665 --> 00:06:05.665
Immediately.

00:06:06.185 --> 00:06:07.385
Immediately.

00:06:07.985 --> 00:06:09.985
Where did you bury the woman?

00:06:11.145 --> 00:06:13.345
After I was released yesterday,
the police have been following me.

00:06:13.425 --> 00:06:14.945
I'll dig out the body now.

00:06:15.625 --> 00:06:17.065
Did I tell you to do that?

00:06:18.185 --> 00:06:19.505
Are you dumb?

00:06:19.585 --> 00:06:21.305
Then, I won't dig the body out. I…

00:06:21.385 --> 00:06:22.825
Burn it. Destroy it.

00:06:22.905 --> 00:06:25.265
Dissolve it. Deal with it.

00:06:25.345 --> 00:06:26.385
Okay.

00:06:32.385 --> 00:06:34.785
Take a picture before you get rid of it.

00:06:34.865 --> 00:06:35.905
Okay.

00:06:46.345 --> 00:06:47.545
AUTO MAINTENANCE, REPAIR SHOP

00:06:47.625 --> 00:06:48.785
Mr. Song.

00:06:48.865 --> 00:06:50.425
The officer from yesterday
is still waiting outside.

00:06:50.505 --> 00:06:52.065
What if he follows me?

00:06:52.145 --> 00:06:55.425
You made a mess and you expect me
to clean up after you?

00:07:02.585 --> 00:07:05.305
If you fail to handle this properly
and the police find out,

00:07:05.385 --> 00:07:06.625
you'll turn yourself in.

00:07:08.065 --> 00:07:09.145
Otherwise,

00:07:10.665 --> 00:07:12.305
I'll make your family disappear.

00:07:21.065 --> 00:07:22.985
Let's see how long you can stay in there.

00:07:28.585 --> 00:07:30.705
QINGSONG CEMENT FACTORY, WEIYANG CITY

00:07:36.105 --> 00:07:39.065
I'M BRINGING XIAOHE TO YUANLONGLI. RAN

00:07:39.145 --> 00:07:40.465
Yuanlongli?

00:07:41.985 --> 00:07:43.665
Why that place of all places?

00:07:43.745 --> 00:07:46.345
QINGSONG CEMENT FACTORY, WEIYANG CITY

00:07:57.225 --> 00:07:58.305
Stop!

00:08:01.825 --> 00:08:02.665
XINFENG AUTO REPAIR

00:08:11.905 --> 00:08:14.065
Who told you to do this? You jerk!

00:08:14.665 --> 00:08:15.545
Asshole!

00:08:17.385 --> 00:08:18.905
Hey! Hey!

00:08:19.505 --> 00:08:21.545
Song Qingsong, you son of…

00:08:29.785 --> 00:08:31.025
Careful, Xiaohe.

00:08:37.305 --> 00:08:38.545
Xiaohe.

00:08:38.625 --> 00:08:39.545
Slow down.

00:08:41.024 --> 00:08:43.185
Red, orange, yellow, green,

00:08:43.264 --> 00:08:44.385
green, blue, purple.

00:08:44.985 --> 00:08:46.785
Everyone is here.

00:09:13.185 --> 00:09:14.985
Big butt!

00:09:17.105 --> 00:09:18.865
-Big butt!
-What are you doing?

00:09:23.305 --> 00:09:24.345
Let go!

00:09:24.425 --> 00:09:25.705
Let go!

00:09:31.585 --> 00:09:33.265
Rat! Pickpocket! Money-grubber!

00:09:33.345 --> 00:09:36.585
How come everywhere we go,
we always see you?

00:09:36.665 --> 00:09:38.265
It's you again?

00:09:38.865 --> 00:09:41.025
Mr. Qian. She is asking your question.

00:09:41.105 --> 00:09:42.545
Officer Ran,

00:09:43.145 --> 00:09:47.025
someone complained about a stench.

00:09:47.105 --> 00:09:48.425
So, I came up here to check.

00:09:48.505 --> 00:09:52.705
I thought someone
must have planted something.

00:09:52.785 --> 00:09:55.185
Who knew that someone
was raising chickens here?

00:09:55.265 --> 00:09:56.305
Unbelievable.

00:09:58.185 --> 00:09:59.865
Why did you enter the chicken coop then?

00:10:00.985 --> 00:10:02.625
To count the chickens.

00:10:02.705 --> 00:10:04.905
How can I fine them without knowing
how many chickens are here?

00:10:05.505 --> 00:10:07.585
I'll get someone from the management here.

00:10:07.665 --> 00:10:08.905
This is unbelievable.

00:10:09.505 --> 00:10:11.185
Unbelievable! I must clean it!

00:10:13.505 --> 00:10:15.585
The chicken coop needs to be removed.

00:10:15.665 --> 00:10:16.625
Qian!

00:10:16.705 --> 00:10:19.545
-How dare you!
-Sir.

00:10:20.265 --> 00:10:21.105
Sir.

00:10:22.785 --> 00:10:23.705
What are you doing?

00:10:25.905 --> 00:10:26.865
Qian Dajun.

00:10:26.945 --> 00:10:27.785
Calm down.

00:10:27.865 --> 00:10:29.385
Let me make myself clear today.

00:10:29.465 --> 00:10:32.265
Touch my chickens
and I'll chop off your hands.

00:10:32.945 --> 00:10:34.225
Sir. Calm down.

00:10:34.305 --> 00:10:35.625
There's an officer here.

00:10:35.705 --> 00:10:37.025
-Calm down.
-I don't care!

00:10:37.105 --> 00:10:38.705
-Calm down. Calm down.
-Stay right there.

00:10:38.785 --> 00:10:40.665
-Stay right there.
-Calm down.

00:10:43.345 --> 00:10:44.425
Calm down.

00:10:45.345 --> 00:10:46.705
-That jerk.
-Calm down.

00:10:49.065 --> 00:10:51.505
Mister, you're amazing.

00:10:51.585 --> 00:10:54.345
Did you raise all these colorful chickens?

00:10:57.145 --> 00:11:00.225
Yes. Little girl, do you like them?

00:11:00.745 --> 00:11:03.105
If you like them, I can give you one.

00:11:03.185 --> 00:11:04.705
Thanks, mister.

00:11:08.905 --> 00:11:12.305
Forget about it.
My mother won't let me raise it.

00:11:13.345 --> 00:11:14.385
Give me a moment.

00:11:35.785 --> 00:11:37.145
Thank you, mister.

00:11:38.425 --> 00:11:41.425
I wonder what color this chick will be.

00:11:41.505 --> 00:11:42.425
Hey!

00:11:43.185 --> 00:11:44.505
It's a raw egg!

00:12:06.945 --> 00:12:11.185
DANFENG MIDDLE SCHOOL

00:12:11.265 --> 00:12:13.225
PRINCIPAL'S ROOM

00:12:17.705 --> 00:12:19.225
Officer He, this is the place.

00:12:19.305 --> 00:12:20.185
Thank you.

00:12:20.265 --> 00:12:21.265
You're welcome.

00:12:22.545 --> 00:12:23.585
Come in.

00:12:24.585 --> 00:12:27.065
Hello, Principal Qin. I am He Xiaohe.

00:12:27.145 --> 00:12:28.985
I'm here for Han Zi'ang.

00:12:29.065 --> 00:12:29.945
Oh.

00:12:30.465 --> 00:12:32.585
Officer He. Take a seat.

00:12:32.665 --> 00:12:33.785
Thank you.

00:12:36.505 --> 00:12:40.345
Principal Qin, I know you're a busy man,
so I'll keep it brief.

00:12:40.425 --> 00:12:44.665
I came to urge you
to reconsider the decision

00:12:44.745 --> 00:12:46.825
to expel Han Zi'ang.

00:12:47.705 --> 00:12:48.865
Officer He.

00:12:48.945 --> 00:12:51.345
I already explained to you clearly

00:12:51.425 --> 00:12:53.545
in our phone call yesterday.

00:12:54.505 --> 00:12:59.185
It's a decision that we made
upon deliberate consideration.

00:12:59.265 --> 00:13:00.385
But…

00:13:01.105 --> 00:13:02.945
Please let me finish.

00:13:03.825 --> 00:13:05.825
The expulsion isn't my decision.

00:13:06.505 --> 00:13:10.025
In class, Han Zi'ang dozes off often.

00:13:10.105 --> 00:13:12.585
And he often misses classes
for no reason at all.

00:13:12.665 --> 00:13:15.305
This time, instead of truancy,

00:13:15.905 --> 00:13:18.345
he stabbed someone outside.

00:13:18.425 --> 00:13:21.785
Principal Qin, does Han Zi'ang
have a history of violence?

00:13:23.465 --> 00:13:24.465
Not that I know of.

00:13:25.145 --> 00:13:29.465
His homeroom teacher told us
that he was usually quiet.

00:13:29.985 --> 00:13:34.465
But you know, the quiet one
turns out to be the most volatile.

00:13:34.545 --> 00:13:35.785
This is just a stereotype.

00:13:36.465 --> 00:13:39.585
From what I was told,
Han Zi'ang is indeed an introvert.

00:13:39.665 --> 00:13:41.345
But that's because he likes to read.

00:13:41.425 --> 00:13:44.705
Of course, what he reads are comic books.

00:13:44.785 --> 00:13:48.825
Perhaps he mixed
fictional elements with reality.

00:13:49.625 --> 00:13:51.825
When he heard that Yuanlongli was haunted,

00:13:51.905 --> 00:13:53.865
he went on an adventure.

00:13:53.945 --> 00:13:55.465
He ran into a homeless guy,

00:13:56.065 --> 00:13:59.185
and then maybe, he was anxious and scared.

00:13:59.265 --> 00:14:02.065
So, he stabbed him to defend himself.

00:14:02.145 --> 00:14:08.705
Officer He, you're saying
that Han Zi'ang acted out of self-defense.

00:14:09.225 --> 00:14:10.225
I get that.

00:14:10.825 --> 00:14:13.145
But the parents don't get that.

00:14:13.225 --> 00:14:14.465
He stabbed someone.

00:14:14.545 --> 00:14:15.745
That's the truth.

00:14:15.825 --> 00:14:17.865
If he comes to school,

00:14:17.945 --> 00:14:20.745
the other parents will be worried sick.

00:14:23.465 --> 00:14:27.905
He is still unconscious in the hospital.

00:14:27.985 --> 00:14:31.305
The police are doing their best
to investigate the case.

00:14:31.385 --> 00:14:33.505
Before the truth comes out,

00:14:33.585 --> 00:14:36.425
I urge the school not to give up on him.

00:14:37.345 --> 00:14:39.705
If someone lends him a hand
at a time like this,

00:14:40.305 --> 00:14:42.305
you're not just saving his education,

00:14:43.065 --> 00:14:44.745
you're saving his life.

00:14:46.305 --> 00:14:47.545
Principal Qin.

00:14:48.185 --> 00:14:49.265
In fact,

00:14:50.465 --> 00:14:53.465
I was worse and more rebellious
than he was back then.

00:14:53.545 --> 00:14:58.065
But someone in my life
never gave up on me.

00:14:58.145 --> 00:15:03.345
He pulled me back in time
and saved my life.

00:15:03.425 --> 00:15:06.065
That's why I can be
an officer like I am now.

00:15:07.465 --> 00:15:10.225
Principal Qin, for a child,

00:15:11.145 --> 00:15:14.585
one decision can determine his whole life.

00:15:14.665 --> 00:15:18.425
I urge you to reconsider.

00:15:19.505 --> 00:15:23.505
Perhaps you can be the one
who saves Han Zi'ang.

00:15:27.105 --> 00:15:30.065
Officer He, how about this?

00:15:30.665 --> 00:15:33.065
Since Han Zi'ang is still unconscious,

00:15:33.145 --> 00:15:36.305
we'll delay his expulsion
as much as possible.

00:15:36.905 --> 00:15:38.545
Before the investigation comes to an end,

00:15:38.625 --> 00:15:40.465
I can speak on behalf of the school

00:15:41.265 --> 00:15:44.425
that if the police
provide proof that Han Zi'ang

00:15:44.505 --> 00:15:47.905
acted out of self-defense,

00:15:47.985 --> 00:15:50.465
then we can reconsider the expulsion.

00:15:51.985 --> 00:15:52.865
Okay.

00:15:52.945 --> 00:15:53.825
Thank you.

00:15:53.905 --> 00:15:55.625
Thank you, Principal Qin.

00:16:06.865 --> 00:16:10.185
Even at this age, Xiaohe is still a rebel.

00:16:10.265 --> 00:16:13.825
She just swallows whatever hardships.

00:16:13.905 --> 00:16:17.665
Sir, Xiaohe is almost like my junior.

00:16:17.745 --> 00:16:19.585
She studied for six years
to be a criminal police officer.

00:16:19.665 --> 00:16:20.745
Have faith in her.

00:16:21.425 --> 00:16:23.505
She's my daughter.
Of course, I have faith in her.

00:16:23.585 --> 00:16:25.465
I'm her dad, after all.

00:16:26.945 --> 00:16:28.865
She also grew up under your nose.

00:16:28.945 --> 00:16:30.905
But this is her first case.

00:16:30.985 --> 00:16:33.225
She needs all the support she can have.

00:16:35.425 --> 00:16:37.385
It was my first case back then too.

00:16:37.465 --> 00:16:39.465
But you didn't pamper me.

00:16:41.305 --> 00:16:42.345
Nonsense!

00:16:42.425 --> 00:16:44.425
Did you acknowledge me
as your mentor back then?

00:16:46.545 --> 00:16:49.225
The older you are,
the more grudges you hold.

00:16:55.705 --> 00:16:58.065
NOTICE, YUANLONGLI INTERNATIONAL
GARDEN REDEVELOPMENT MEETING

00:16:58.145 --> 00:17:00.265
THE MEETING WILL BE HELD AT 1 P.M. TODAY.

00:17:14.944 --> 00:17:16.704
Why did they seal it off?

00:17:17.944 --> 00:17:20.385
That side wasn't involved.
Why seal that place?

00:17:20.464 --> 00:17:21.665
Let's go, sir.

00:17:21.745 --> 00:17:23.905
SEALED, NANSHAN BRANCH
WEIYANG PUBLIC SECURITY BUREAU

00:17:25.905 --> 00:17:27.345
I don't think we'll find anything here.

00:17:28.105 --> 00:17:29.625
Should we go to the surveillance room?

00:17:30.825 --> 00:17:31.905
Sir.

00:17:32.425 --> 00:17:34.585
The surveillance room
was demolished a long time ago.

00:17:34.665 --> 00:17:35.585
You already know about that.

00:17:36.745 --> 00:17:37.705
Oh.

00:17:39.025 --> 00:17:40.265
Then, let's head
to the underground car park.

00:17:40.905 --> 00:17:42.225
I bet you have no idea

00:17:42.305 --> 00:17:45.025
what it has become after all these years.

00:17:45.105 --> 00:17:47.425
Sir, let's leave.

00:17:47.505 --> 00:17:49.025
Just stay out of the case.

00:17:49.545 --> 00:17:50.865
If this turns out to be a prank…

00:17:50.945 --> 00:17:53.705
Eighteen years ago,
they also said the Xu Meng case

00:17:53.785 --> 00:17:54.905
was a prank.

00:17:54.985 --> 00:17:56.345
What did you do?

00:18:04.185 --> 00:18:06.825
Sir, just tell the truth.

00:18:10.065 --> 00:18:11.985
You want to keep me here in Weiyang

00:18:12.065 --> 00:18:14.385
to investigate the case 18 years ago.

00:18:21.865 --> 00:18:23.705
Qiao lives in Yuanlongli.

00:18:24.225 --> 00:18:25.385
Don't you want to see her?

00:18:39.825 --> 00:18:40.985
Officer Ran.

00:18:41.945 --> 00:18:42.985
Qiao.

00:18:43.505 --> 00:18:45.105
Sorry to disturb you again.

00:18:47.945 --> 00:18:48.785
And this is…

00:18:48.865 --> 00:18:51.385
Hi, miss. I am He Xiaohe.

00:18:51.465 --> 00:18:53.465
My father is He Yuanhang.

00:18:53.545 --> 00:18:55.585
He works with Uncle Ran.

00:18:56.545 --> 00:18:58.665
Hi, Xiaohe. I am Qiao Suqing.

00:18:58.745 --> 00:18:59.665
It's nice to meet you.

00:19:02.105 --> 00:19:03.825
Miss, you're so pretty.

00:19:03.905 --> 00:19:07.345
No wonder Uncle Ran
brought me here specifically.

00:19:13.505 --> 00:19:15.305
Come. Come in.

00:19:16.505 --> 00:19:17.785
Change your shoes.

00:19:40.425 --> 00:19:41.305
Xiaohe.

00:19:41.385 --> 00:19:42.985
What do you want to drink?

00:19:43.065 --> 00:19:44.545
-This one.
-This one?

00:19:45.785 --> 00:19:46.985
Then, Officer Ran…

00:19:47.705 --> 00:19:48.625
Thank you.

00:19:49.385 --> 00:19:51.505
-Here.
-Thank you.

00:19:55.905 --> 00:19:58.745
Miss, your house is so clean.

00:19:58.825 --> 00:19:59.745
And it smells good too.

00:20:00.545 --> 00:20:01.865
Thank you, Xiaohe.

00:20:01.945 --> 00:20:03.025
I'm living alone.

00:20:03.105 --> 00:20:05.425
When I'm free, I like to clean my house.

00:20:05.505 --> 00:20:07.265
You're living alone?

00:20:07.345 --> 00:20:08.745
Do you have a boyfriend?

00:20:11.945 --> 00:20:12.785
No.

00:20:13.745 --> 00:20:15.225
From what I know,

00:20:15.305 --> 00:20:18.105
Uncle Ran doesn't have
a girlfriend either.

00:20:23.865 --> 00:20:25.905
Don't get me wrong.

00:20:25.985 --> 00:20:28.305
I'm just telling facts.

00:20:36.865 --> 00:20:37.985
Xiaohe.

00:20:38.065 --> 00:20:39.505
Go take a shower here.

00:20:39.585 --> 00:20:40.865
I'll come back later
to pick you up. All right?

00:20:40.945 --> 00:20:43.545
No. I have to explore the maze with you.

00:20:43.625 --> 00:20:44.705
You must stay here.

00:20:44.785 --> 00:20:46.265
Look at you now.

00:20:46.345 --> 00:20:47.985
When your father comes here,
how am I supposed to hand you back to him?

00:20:51.185 --> 00:20:52.225
Come.

00:20:52.305 --> 00:20:54.945
Xiaohe. Let's get you
all cleaned up, okay?

00:20:56.025 --> 00:20:57.465
Officer Ran, don't let me keep you.

00:20:57.545 --> 00:20:59.025
I'll take care of Xiaohe.

00:20:59.105 --> 00:21:00.185
Don't worry.

00:21:01.425 --> 00:21:02.265
Thank you.

00:21:03.105 --> 00:21:04.905
Uncle Ran, you're blushing.

00:21:07.145 --> 00:21:08.345
Am I?

00:21:09.425 --> 00:21:11.225
Let's go to the shower.

00:21:26.745 --> 00:21:27.985
Officer He.

00:21:28.945 --> 00:21:30.185
What happened to you?

00:21:30.265 --> 00:21:31.625
Is the case almost over?

00:21:31.705 --> 00:21:34.545
I'm waiting for my tip-off reward.

00:21:35.385 --> 00:21:36.465
So am I.

00:21:38.265 --> 00:21:40.345
Please supervise the young one well.

00:21:40.425 --> 00:21:43.425
Don't let him
get carried away by his needs.

00:21:43.945 --> 00:21:44.825
Young one? Who?

00:21:44.905 --> 00:21:46.065
Officer Ran.

00:21:46.585 --> 00:21:49.745
I keep seeing him visiting Unit 415.

00:21:49.825 --> 00:21:51.905
A mistress lives there.

00:21:52.665 --> 00:21:53.705
Don't make things up.

00:21:53.785 --> 00:21:54.945
I didn't.

00:21:55.025 --> 00:21:57.425
I just saw him take a little girl

00:21:57.505 --> 00:21:59.545
to the mistress's home.

00:22:05.625 --> 00:22:08.225
Du, if you are bored,

00:22:08.305 --> 00:22:11.865
study how the amazing detectives
solve the cases in your detective novels.

00:22:11.945 --> 00:22:14.385
Don't just stare at your neighbors
and spread rumors.

00:22:14.465 --> 00:22:15.745
But I…

00:22:17.585 --> 00:22:18.625
You told me

00:22:18.705 --> 00:22:20.825
to give you useful information,
didn't you?

00:22:21.665 --> 00:22:22.865
I can't believe it.

00:22:25.185 --> 00:22:26.905
Come. Eat while it's warm.

00:22:26.985 --> 00:22:27.945
Wow!

00:22:28.625 --> 00:22:29.865
Ms. Qiao.

00:22:29.945 --> 00:22:33.905
You're just like a real-life super nanny.

00:22:34.665 --> 00:22:36.265
You're a smooth-talker.

00:22:36.345 --> 00:22:37.305
Dig in.

00:22:43.705 --> 00:22:44.665
What's the matter?

00:22:45.625 --> 00:22:48.825
It'd be great if I could call you
auntie in the future.

00:22:49.985 --> 00:22:51.745
Witty, aren't you?

00:22:52.385 --> 00:22:55.305
I've never thought
of Officer Ran that way.

00:22:56.185 --> 00:22:57.025
You're lying.

00:22:57.705 --> 00:22:59.145
I'm telling the truth.

00:22:59.225 --> 00:23:01.825
I was just saying
I'd like to call you auntie.

00:23:01.905 --> 00:23:04.505
Why did you think of Uncle Ran right away?

00:23:06.345 --> 00:23:07.345
How dare you!

00:23:10.025 --> 00:23:11.025
Coming.

00:23:13.145 --> 00:23:15.905
You can't wait to see him.

00:23:21.425 --> 00:23:22.265
You're…

00:23:22.345 --> 00:23:23.225
Dad!

00:23:24.825 --> 00:23:25.985
Xiaohe.

00:23:26.745 --> 00:23:28.745
Officer He. Come in.

00:23:28.825 --> 00:23:30.705
It's okay. I'm all dusty.

00:23:30.785 --> 00:23:32.505
-I'm here to pick my kid up.
-It's okay.

00:23:32.585 --> 00:23:34.665
Dad, I went inside
a chicken coop just now.

00:23:34.745 --> 00:23:36.385
Did you go inside a pigsty or something?

00:23:36.465 --> 00:23:39.065
I didn't get into a pigsty,
but I was harassed by pigs.

00:23:39.945 --> 00:23:41.465
Officer He. Please come in.

00:23:41.545 --> 00:23:42.545
Let me get you a fresh towel.

00:23:43.465 --> 00:23:44.585
Sorry about that.

00:23:49.385 --> 00:23:51.705
You even took a shower. Where's Uncle Ran?

00:23:51.785 --> 00:23:54.705
He's solving the maze on the 18th floor.

00:23:54.785 --> 00:23:57.305
Ms. Qiao's shampoo smells so good.

00:23:57.385 --> 00:23:58.745
Her egg noodles are delicious too.

00:23:58.825 --> 00:24:02.225
Dad, you must thank her
for taking good care of me.

00:24:04.625 --> 00:24:06.305
Here, Officer He. Clean yourself.

00:24:06.385 --> 00:24:07.345
Sure. Thank you.

00:24:07.425 --> 00:24:09.105
My daughter must have troubled you a lot.

00:24:09.185 --> 00:24:11.745
Not at all. She's so obedient.

00:24:12.585 --> 00:24:13.585
Officer He, do stay here.

00:24:13.665 --> 00:24:16.625
It's okay. I'll just wipe myself quickly.

00:24:19.545 --> 00:24:21.905
Dad, I love Ms. Qiao.

00:24:21.985 --> 00:24:25.025
Can Uncle Ran bring me here often?

00:24:28.545 --> 00:24:31.065
Go. Wash the towel for Ms. Qiao.

00:24:49.425 --> 00:24:50.385
Thank you.

00:24:54.425 --> 00:24:55.345
Officer He,

00:24:55.945 --> 00:24:59.305
I know I have a bad reputation

00:24:59.825 --> 00:25:02.745
and that I should stay away
from Officer Ran.

00:25:05.945 --> 00:25:10.305
But I am not what they say I am.

00:25:15.225 --> 00:25:17.265
I only trust what I see with my own eyes.

00:25:17.345 --> 00:25:20.345
Don't take those rumors to heart.

00:25:21.065 --> 00:25:22.825
If you have done nothing wrong,

00:25:22.905 --> 00:25:26.145
there's no need
to worry about false rumors.

00:25:37.785 --> 00:25:40.625
COME TO THE OPPOSITE
OF THE FOOT MASSAGE PARLOR QUICKLY, LILI

00:25:45.065 --> 00:25:47.065
Do you have to make a call?

00:25:47.145 --> 00:25:48.465
You can use my line.

00:25:49.345 --> 00:25:50.185
It's okay.

00:25:51.065 --> 00:25:54.225
Can I trouble you
to look after Xiaohe for a while?

00:25:54.305 --> 00:25:55.785
I might have to pick her up later.

00:25:55.865 --> 00:25:57.065
Sure. No trouble at all.

00:25:57.145 --> 00:25:59.905
I couldn't be happier that Xiaohe is here.

00:26:00.745 --> 00:26:02.265
Me too.

00:26:03.185 --> 00:26:04.345
Look at her.

00:26:04.425 --> 00:26:05.465
Be a good girl.

00:26:06.545 --> 00:26:07.985
Thank you so much.

00:26:13.665 --> 00:26:17.545
FLEA MARKET

00:26:37.865 --> 00:26:40.665
THE USUAL PLACE TONIGHT AT EIGHT
SEE YOU

00:26:53.785 --> 00:26:55.225
What do you want?

00:26:55.305 --> 00:26:57.025
Look at the car plate.

00:26:57.545 --> 00:27:00.385
I am the deputy manager
at Qingsong Cement Factory.

00:27:01.025 --> 00:27:03.825
Thugs like you best not touch me.

00:27:07.105 --> 00:27:09.425
-I'm looking for you, you punk.
-For what?

00:27:09.505 --> 00:27:12.745
A guy of mine, Wolfie,

00:27:12.825 --> 00:27:14.585
was arrested by the police two days ago.

00:27:14.665 --> 00:27:16.265
Do you know what happened?

00:27:16.345 --> 00:27:17.185
No idea.

00:27:19.585 --> 00:27:20.985
Do you know or not?

00:27:21.065 --> 00:27:23.185
Yes. I know.

00:27:25.785 --> 00:27:26.625
I know.

00:27:28.265 --> 00:27:29.425
Your guy didn't kill anyone.

00:27:29.505 --> 00:27:30.745
Don't tell me everything.

00:27:32.425 --> 00:27:34.305
Just answer my question.

00:27:35.105 --> 00:27:35.945
Okay.

00:27:36.665 --> 00:27:39.225
Did Song Qingsong make the offer?

00:27:40.105 --> 00:27:41.145
No.

00:27:41.225 --> 00:27:42.185
I did.

00:27:43.065 --> 00:27:44.825
I can swear on my life. I made the offer.

00:27:45.425 --> 00:27:46.665
I'm trying to become clean, you know?

00:27:48.225 --> 00:27:49.505
Since you made the offer,

00:27:50.625 --> 00:27:51.505
pay up.

00:27:52.265 --> 00:27:53.345
Pay what?

00:27:53.425 --> 00:27:55.465
Your guy didn't even finish the job.

00:27:55.545 --> 00:27:56.905
Why should I pay up?

00:27:58.265 --> 00:27:59.705
Why? Why?

00:28:01.585 --> 00:28:03.065
Did I tell you to do that?

00:28:03.145 --> 00:28:05.145
Let's just be civil.

00:28:05.225 --> 00:28:06.385
Be professional.

00:28:09.105 --> 00:28:13.345
My guy is an important person
in the company.

00:28:13.865 --> 00:28:17.625
And because of you, he was arrested
and is still not yet released.

00:28:18.385 --> 00:28:21.105
Should we calculate the loss of profit?

00:28:21.185 --> 00:28:22.705
The loss of profit?

00:28:23.225 --> 00:28:25.345
Your guy didn't finish the job.

00:28:25.425 --> 00:28:29.105
I had to clean up after him
and deal with those two.

00:28:30.225 --> 00:28:31.745
You killed them?

00:28:32.945 --> 00:28:33.785
Right.

00:28:35.825 --> 00:28:38.385
I didn't know you were this ruthless.

00:28:38.465 --> 00:28:39.985
One slash, one life.

00:28:41.225 --> 00:28:42.385
Not bad.

00:28:42.465 --> 00:28:44.705
What about my loss of profit?

00:28:48.665 --> 00:28:49.865
That's easy.

00:28:51.785 --> 00:28:54.225
We won't extort each other.

00:28:55.105 --> 00:28:56.865
Aren't you the second in command
of the cement factory?

00:28:58.225 --> 00:28:59.305
That's an important position.

00:29:00.025 --> 00:29:03.705
Sign a contractor agreement with me
worth 300,000 yuan.

00:29:03.785 --> 00:29:04.705
You're the client.

00:29:04.785 --> 00:29:05.665
I'm the contractor.

00:29:06.265 --> 00:29:07.105
Good enough?

00:29:07.945 --> 00:29:09.985
Maybe we can just settle
the balance instead.

00:29:14.625 --> 00:29:16.585
-Will you sign it or not?
-Yes!

00:29:16.665 --> 00:29:18.145
Yes. Yes.

00:29:24.265 --> 00:29:28.225
I like how decisive you are, Mr. Wu.

00:29:35.185 --> 00:29:36.025
CONTRACTOR AGREEMENT

00:29:36.105 --> 00:29:37.425
CLIENT: WU SHANLONG
CONTRACTOR: JIN MANSHAN

00:29:40.465 --> 00:29:43.025
Tell them to tell Manlang.

00:29:43.545 --> 00:29:44.385
Okay.

00:29:47.705 --> 00:29:48.745
Speak.

00:29:49.665 --> 00:29:53.065
Ms. Zhao forbids us
from mentioning Mengmeng.

00:29:53.145 --> 00:29:55.785
My friends and I only gossip in secret.

00:29:56.305 --> 00:29:58.865
They think a client is suspicious.

00:30:00.425 --> 00:30:01.225
Who?

00:30:02.345 --> 00:30:04.745
When he came, he only asked for Mengmeng.

00:30:04.825 --> 00:30:06.585
And he paid double.

00:30:06.665 --> 00:30:08.185
We call him Mr. Sun.

00:30:08.265 --> 00:30:09.345
Mr. Sun?

00:30:09.985 --> 00:30:12.865
He was already a regular at Pattia.

00:30:12.945 --> 00:30:15.825
And he always came with a bag
of branded clothes.

00:30:15.905 --> 00:30:18.225
The brands inside were so expensive.

00:30:19.545 --> 00:30:20.985
Branded clothes.

00:30:22.265 --> 00:30:23.505
Double Fish.

00:30:24.025 --> 00:30:25.265
It's expensive.

00:30:26.585 --> 00:30:27.585
Bowls.

00:30:28.545 --> 00:30:31.465
This dress is probably
worth more than this unit.

00:30:35.505 --> 00:30:38.465
Did Mr. Sun hand out goods
from Bowls and Double Fish?

00:30:39.665 --> 00:30:42.145
Bowls and Double Fish…

00:30:43.905 --> 00:30:45.305
I can't remember.

00:30:47.265 --> 00:30:48.985
What is Mr. Sun's real name?

00:30:49.985 --> 00:30:50.905
I'm not sure.

00:30:53.265 --> 00:30:56.745
But after Mengmeng went missing,
Mr. Sun stopped showing up.

00:31:03.305 --> 00:31:07.705
Sir, I've told you what I know.

00:31:07.785 --> 00:31:10.345
I hope you can find Mengmeng soon.

00:31:10.425 --> 00:31:11.905
I'm quite worried about her.

00:31:13.105 --> 00:31:15.305
Don't worry. We've been searching for her.

00:31:15.385 --> 00:31:16.705
Your information is very important.

00:31:16.785 --> 00:31:18.465
Thank you, Lili.

00:31:18.545 --> 00:31:21.505
If there's nothing else, I have to go now.

00:31:23.905 --> 00:31:24.625
A HOME VISIT TO XU MENG’S UNCLE,
QIAO GUOQIANG.

00:31:24.705 --> 00:31:25.465
CLEAR MARKS ON THE FLOOR
BY THE FOOT OF THE BED,

00:31:25.545 --> 00:31:26.265
INDICATING IT HAS BEEN MOVED.

00:31:28.865 --> 00:31:29.825
Oh.

00:31:29.905 --> 00:31:32.585
When I was at Pattia,
a woman called Zhizhi

00:31:32.665 --> 00:31:34.505
was quite close to Mr. Sun.

00:31:34.585 --> 00:31:36.225
You can look for her.

00:31:42.825 --> 00:31:44.145
Zhizhi.

00:31:45.985 --> 00:31:47.145
Su Yuzhi.

00:31:49.385 --> 00:31:50.985
A rich guy? What's his name?

00:31:51.065 --> 00:31:52.985
Sun, I think.

00:31:53.065 --> 00:31:54.265
His name?

00:31:55.265 --> 00:31:56.465
I don't know.

00:32:00.465 --> 00:32:02.065
She lied.

00:32:29.065 --> 00:32:30.705
Adult Gaokao…

00:32:32.305 --> 00:32:34.545
I thought only students sit for exams.

00:32:34.625 --> 00:32:37.025
Adults have to do it too?

00:32:37.705 --> 00:32:39.465
It's adult gaokao.

00:32:39.545 --> 00:32:42.145
It's a chance for people like me
who never went to high school

00:32:42.225 --> 00:32:43.945
to enter a university.

00:32:44.025 --> 00:32:47.065
Oh. You want to impress Uncle Ran.

00:32:48.185 --> 00:32:50.225
You're teasing me again.

00:32:51.505 --> 00:32:54.745
Officer Ran is an ace student
from a prestigious school.

00:32:55.585 --> 00:32:59.745
I started working after junior high.

00:33:01.265 --> 00:33:03.145
So, I could only perform

00:33:04.465 --> 00:33:06.385
physical labor,
like taking care of someone.

00:33:06.465 --> 00:33:09.625
That's why I want to study hard,

00:33:09.705 --> 00:33:12.905
get a degree, and find a good job.

00:33:13.505 --> 00:33:16.305
-You can do this.
-Why do you say so?

00:33:16.385 --> 00:33:19.025
Because you are the hardworking Ms. Qiao.

00:33:19.105 --> 00:33:23.425
My mom told me that hard work
could make your dreams come true.

00:33:24.705 --> 00:33:26.105
Your mom is right.

00:33:30.585 --> 00:33:32.425
I, too, have to study hard.

00:33:36.505 --> 00:33:39.345
-Do you even understand it?
-That's why I have to study.

00:33:39.425 --> 00:33:42.625
I want to be an ace student
like Uncle Ran.

00:33:43.785 --> 00:33:45.665
Then, let's have a pinky promise.

00:33:45.745 --> 00:33:48.225
We will both
be ace students in the future.

00:33:48.305 --> 00:33:49.425
Sure.

00:33:50.705 --> 00:33:52.225
You make a pinky promise,

00:33:52.305 --> 00:33:54.305
you keep it all your life.

00:33:59.585 --> 00:34:04.585
YUZHI BOUTIQUE

00:34:15.744 --> 00:34:18.425
The latest collection.
Pick anything you like.

00:34:28.304 --> 00:34:29.344
Excuse me.

00:34:34.385 --> 00:34:36.985
Cutie. You're finally here.

00:34:37.065 --> 00:34:38.705
Are you here to treat me to hotpot?

00:34:39.505 --> 00:34:40.625
No.

00:34:41.304 --> 00:34:44.185
I'm here to ask you about Mr. Sun.

00:34:44.705 --> 00:34:46.465
You said you weren't
close to him last time.

00:34:46.545 --> 00:34:47.505
You lied.

00:34:49.465 --> 00:34:52.225
Without lying, how else
could I make you come to me?

00:34:54.545 --> 00:34:55.545
It's a game of flirting.

00:34:56.145 --> 00:34:57.305
Su Yuzhi.

00:34:57.385 --> 00:34:58.985
I brought him here.

00:34:59.065 --> 00:35:01.265
So, tell us the truth now.

00:35:01.345 --> 00:35:04.345
Cutie, what truth do you want to hear?

00:35:07.705 --> 00:35:10.065
Please tell me who Mr. Sun is.

00:35:12.025 --> 00:35:15.545
Sun's name is Sun Zhengyong.

00:35:15.625 --> 00:35:16.745
He's from Fujian.

00:35:16.825 --> 00:35:19.345
He has shares in my boutique, too.

00:35:19.425 --> 00:35:20.825
Don't get the wrong idea.

00:35:20.905 --> 00:35:22.825
We are not intimate.

00:35:22.905 --> 00:35:24.985
What about him and Xu Meng?

00:35:28.305 --> 00:35:29.505
If I tell you,

00:35:29.585 --> 00:35:31.345
will you still come to me in the future?

00:35:34.025 --> 00:35:35.785
Please… Please answer my question.

00:35:41.065 --> 00:35:43.185
Did Sun Zhengyong give this dress to you?

00:35:43.265 --> 00:35:44.745
Mind your tongue now.

00:35:48.065 --> 00:35:50.705
I bought it from him. Wholesale.

00:35:54.625 --> 00:35:55.905
FASHION BOUTIQUE

00:35:57.665 --> 00:35:59.665
This is… A counterfeit?

00:35:59.745 --> 00:36:02.145
Counterfeits sell like hot cakes.

00:36:02.225 --> 00:36:05.185
So, Sun Zhengyong
bought the authentic products,

00:36:05.265 --> 00:36:07.185
then made counterfeits
to sell them in wholesale.

00:36:07.785 --> 00:36:09.305
Cutie, you're smart.

00:36:09.385 --> 00:36:11.785
You figured it out.

00:36:16.585 --> 00:36:18.105
How does he deal
with the authentic products?

00:36:18.185 --> 00:36:21.985
Normally, he gives them to girls he likes.

00:36:22.705 --> 00:36:24.625
He gives them to Xu Meng?

00:36:24.705 --> 00:36:25.945
I guess so.

00:36:26.025 --> 00:36:27.385
He likes Mengmeng the most.

00:36:27.465 --> 00:36:30.825
Are you saying Mr. Sun has something to do
with Mengmeng's disappearance?

00:36:31.625 --> 00:36:32.545
What do you think?

00:36:33.745 --> 00:36:34.905
I don't know.

00:36:37.865 --> 00:36:39.665
I saw them argue once.

00:36:40.265 --> 00:36:41.505
When was it? And where?

00:36:41.585 --> 00:36:43.305
At Pattia.

00:36:43.385 --> 00:36:44.905
Mr. Sun was drunk.

00:36:44.985 --> 00:36:48.105
He hugged Mengmeng
and asked her to be his girlfriend.

00:36:48.185 --> 00:36:50.905
Mengmeng said no,
and Mr. Sun lost his patience.

00:36:50.985 --> 00:36:53.145
He said Mengmeng played hard to get
and looked down on him.

00:36:53.225 --> 00:36:54.585
They then argued.

00:36:59.745 --> 00:37:01.545
-And then?
-And then?

00:37:02.545 --> 00:37:04.465
You raided Pattia.

00:37:09.225 --> 00:37:12.705
Is there any place in Weiyang
that sells authentic Bowls dresses?

00:37:12.785 --> 00:37:14.985
It's a huge brand.

00:37:15.065 --> 00:37:16.865
There's one official store in Weiyang.

00:37:16.945 --> 00:37:18.385
Right inside Weiyang Mall.

00:37:18.465 --> 00:37:21.785
Can you give us the wholesale address
of Sun Zhengyong?

00:37:31.865 --> 00:37:33.105
NANMEN WHOLESALE MARKET
NANSHAN DISTRICT, WEIYANG CITY

00:37:33.185 --> 00:37:34.025
FASHION CLOTHING HALL

00:37:36.025 --> 00:37:37.225
Oh.

00:37:41.825 --> 00:37:43.465
Remember the surprise I promised you?

00:37:44.985 --> 00:37:46.665
We have a rule. We can't…

00:37:47.185 --> 00:37:48.705
I know.

00:37:49.585 --> 00:37:51.145
I'll charge you the original price.

00:37:52.025 --> 00:37:53.265
Five yuan.

00:37:57.345 --> 00:37:58.265
Take it.

00:37:59.225 --> 00:38:01.585
If you don't buy it,
she's going to lure you in again.

00:38:10.745 --> 00:38:12.545
Thank you, Su Yuzhi.

00:38:13.065 --> 00:38:14.865
I wish you a prosperous business.

00:38:20.825 --> 00:38:21.905
See you.

00:38:29.145 --> 00:38:30.225
Why not put it on now?

00:38:35.945 --> 00:38:36.785
He.

00:38:37.665 --> 00:38:40.065
I think Su Yuzhi
is telling the truth this time.

00:38:40.665 --> 00:38:41.945
Of course.

00:38:42.025 --> 00:38:43.785
She is so devoted to you.

00:38:43.865 --> 00:38:44.705
He.

00:38:44.785 --> 00:38:46.625
We're investigating a case. Be serious.

00:38:47.825 --> 00:38:48.905
Sure.

00:38:48.985 --> 00:38:51.225
Then, analyze this seriously.

00:38:51.825 --> 00:38:54.905
Perhaps Sun Zhengyong
thought Xu Meng looked down on him.

00:38:56.025 --> 00:38:58.665
His love turned into hatred,
and he killed her.

00:39:05.665 --> 00:39:07.025
YONG'S FASHION

00:39:07.105 --> 00:39:08.945
Let me meet him in his shop.

00:39:09.025 --> 00:39:12.345
I'll visit the official Bowls store
to check when he purchased the dress.

00:39:13.305 --> 00:39:14.545
Not bad.

00:39:14.625 --> 00:39:16.145
You've learned how to narrow down
the scope from me.

00:39:16.745 --> 00:39:17.945
That's progress.

00:39:20.905 --> 00:39:23.785
Also, we shouldn't give up
on the lead on Song Qingsong.

00:39:23.865 --> 00:39:25.745
Be patient. One at a time.

00:40:04.585 --> 00:40:05.425
What happened to your head?

00:40:06.025 --> 00:40:08.385
What could be so serious
that you couldn't say it on the phone?

00:40:09.705 --> 00:40:11.225
What else could it be?

00:40:12.225 --> 00:40:13.265
If it's about Song, forget it.

00:40:15.305 --> 00:40:16.465
Forget it?

00:40:17.265 --> 00:40:19.825
Wu Shanlong. Are you taking me for a fool?

00:40:20.425 --> 00:40:21.705
Two plans.

00:40:21.785 --> 00:40:23.385
And both times,
you told me they were foolproof.

00:40:23.465 --> 00:40:24.745
Then, what happened?

00:40:27.345 --> 00:40:29.665
You're putting it as if it were my fault.

00:40:29.745 --> 00:40:31.385
You came to me first,

00:40:31.465 --> 00:40:33.865
saying that we could work together
to scam money out of Song.

00:40:36.185 --> 00:40:37.505
I don't care about his money anymore.

00:40:38.545 --> 00:40:42.345
Can you even hear what you just said?

00:40:43.905 --> 00:40:45.225
The police are after Mengmeng.

00:40:46.425 --> 00:40:47.945
Song Qingsong wants me to turn myself in.

00:40:51.905 --> 00:40:55.945
So, if you turn yourself in
and they interrogate you,

00:40:56.025 --> 00:40:57.945
will you rat me out?

00:41:04.985 --> 00:41:05.825
I knew it.

00:41:05.905 --> 00:41:09.385
If men were reliable, pigs could fly.

00:41:11.105 --> 00:41:12.825
I was forced to.

00:41:12.905 --> 00:41:14.505
Do you have a plan or not?

00:41:14.585 --> 00:41:16.785
Didn't you just say my plan was useless?

00:41:16.865 --> 00:41:17.745
Zhao Hongmei,

00:41:17.825 --> 00:41:19.905
let me remind you
that we're both in the same boat.

00:41:24.305 --> 00:41:25.905
We're past the point of no return.

00:41:25.985 --> 00:41:27.985
We can't do this forever.

00:41:29.105 --> 00:41:30.305
Wu Shanlong.

00:41:32.505 --> 00:41:34.425
I want you to tell me the truth.

00:41:34.945 --> 00:41:36.305
Otherwise, forget everything.

00:41:36.945 --> 00:41:38.025
Mengmeng.

00:41:39.985 --> 00:41:42.145
Is she dead or alive?

00:41:44.185 --> 00:41:45.385
She's dead.

00:41:46.585 --> 00:41:47.905
Stone cold dead!

00:41:50.665 --> 00:41:52.465
For goodness's sake.